---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Shipping & Service Policy - MSZ Software House">
  <main class="bg-white dark:bg-charcoal-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white tracking-tighter">Shipping & Service Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-charcoal-800/80 dark:text-gray-300">
          Last updated: December 2025
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Overview</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              MSZ Software House specializes in digital products and services. Since we deal with digital deliverables, traditional "shipping" doesn't apply. Instead, we provide instant digital delivery and service execution timelines.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Digital Product Delivery</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Instant Delivery Items</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Canva Templates:</strong> Delivered instantly via download link</li>
              <li><strong>Notion Systems:</strong> Access provided within 15 minutes</li>
              <li><strong>eBooks & Courses:</strong> Download links sent immediately</li>
              <li><strong>Preset Packs:</strong> Instant download after payment confirmation</li>
              <li><strong>Website Templates:</strong> Files delivered within 30 minutes</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Processing Time: Up to 1 Hour</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Social Media Toolkits:</strong> Customized packages</li>
              <li><strong>Automation Workflows:</strong> n8n/Make templates with setup instructions</li>
              <li><strong>Custom Templates:</strong> Modified versions of existing templates</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Delivery Methods</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Email with download links</li>
              <li>WhatsApp file sharing</li>
              <li>Google Drive/Dropbox shared folders</li>
              <li>Direct cloud dashboard access</li>
              <li>Zip file downloads</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">SaaS Subscription Delivery</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Standard Delivery: 2-12 Hours</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              All SaaS subscriptions are sourced legally and ethically. Delivery time depends on:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Service provider verification process</li>
              <li>Account setup and configuration</li>
              <li>Quality assurance testing</li>
              <li>Documentation preparation</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What You Receive</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Login credentials (username/password)</li>
              <li>Access instructions and guidelines</li>
              <li>Service-specific setup guide</li>
              <li>Support contact information</li>
              <li>Terms of use and limitations</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Delivery Guarantee</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>100% legal and legitimate access</li>
              <li>No carding or fraudulent methods</li>
              <li>No VPN tricks or country manipulation</li>
              <li>Official provider compliance</li>
              <li>Working access guaranteed</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Service Delivery Timelines</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Website Development</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Landing Page:</strong> 3-5 business days</li>
              <li><strong>Business Website:</strong> 7-14 business days</li>
              <li><strong>E-commerce Store:</strong> 14-21 business days</li>
              <li><strong>Custom Web App:</strong> 21-45 business days</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Branding & Design</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Logo Design:</strong> 2-3 business days</li>
              <li><strong>Brand Identity:</strong> 5-7 business days</li>
              <li><strong>Social Media Kit:</strong> 3-5 business days</li>
              <li><strong>Complete Branding:</strong> 10-14 business days</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Marketing & Automation</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Marketing Funnel:</strong> 5-10 business days</li>
              <li><strong>Social Media Management Setup:</strong> 2-3 business days</li>
              <li><strong>AI Automation:</strong> 7-14 business days</li>
              <li><strong>SaaS Integration:</strong> 3-7 business days</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Milestone-Based Delivery</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Large projects are delivered in milestones:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Initial concept and wireframes</li>
              <li>Design mockups and approval</li>
              <li>Development and testing</li>
              <li>Final delivery and handover</li>
              <li>Post-delivery support period</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Delivery Confirmation</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">How We Confirm Delivery</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>WhatsApp Confirmation:</strong> Screenshot of delivered files/access</li>
              <li><strong>Email Receipt:</strong> Detailed delivery confirmation</li>
              <li><strong>Access Verification:</strong> We test all credentials before delivery</li>
              <li><strong>Follow-up Support:</strong> 24-48 hours post-delivery check</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Customer Responsibility</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Confirm receipt within 24 hours</li>
              <li>Test access/files immediately</li>
              <li>Report any issues within 48 hours</li>
              <li>Provide feedback for service improvement</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Delivery Issues & Support</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Common Issues</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Email Delivery:</strong> Check spam/junk folders</li>
              <li><strong>Download Links:</strong> Links expire after 7 days</li>
              <li><strong>File Corruption:</strong> We provide immediate replacement</li>
              <li><strong>Access Problems:</strong> 24/7 support available</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Support Channels</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Email:</strong> mszsoftwarehouse@gmail.com (Fastest response)</li>
              <li><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 2-4 hours</li>
              <li><strong>Emergency Support:</strong> Available 24/7</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Quality Assurance</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Before delivery, all products and services undergo:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Quality Testing:</strong> Files checked for corruption/completeness</li>
              <li><strong>Access Verification:</strong> All credentials tested before delivery</li>
              <li><strong>Documentation Review:</strong> Instructions verified for accuracy</li>
              <li><strong>Compatibility Check:</strong> Ensured to work as described</li>
              <li><strong>Final Approval:</strong> Senior team member approval required</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">International Customers</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              We serve customers globally with the same delivery standards:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>No additional delivery charges for digital products</li>
              <li>Same delivery timeframes regardless of location</li>
              <li>Multi-timezone support availability</li>
              <li>English language support for all deliveries</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-cream-100 dark:bg-charcoal-800 rounded-lg border border-cream-400 dark:border-charcoal-700">
            <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-center">
              Our commitment: Fast, reliable, and professional delivery of all digital products and services.<br>
              Last updated: December 2025 | Â© 2025 MSZ Software House. All rights reserved.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>